				\begin{document}$$\alpha =0.05$$\end{document}α=0.05 for all statistical tests. The proportion of between-clusters variance over the total variance explained by each trait was evaluated (Supplementary Table S6). Trait ‘caryopsis width’ explained the most variance among clusters (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
